{"tid":444134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華裔律師出書教合法赴美生子： 好似去美國shopping一樣坦蕩","createTime":"2017-10-22T08:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T23:36:48.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c091c44b507ced208cb1585fb40b034ace58c75c","tid":444134,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T08:51:48.000Z","msg":"中國孕婦赴北美產子情況屢見不鮮，近十年有越來越多趨勢。在氣候宜人的南加州，更是集中全美八成華人月子中心，2015年美國聯邦政府大力掃蕩月子中心，令到當中的孕婦陷被起訴危機。到底赴美產子是否合法？月子中心當中會否有灰色地帶？美國洛杉磯華人律師劉龍珠最近出版新書《川普時代如何合法赴美生子及代孕》希望剖析法律層面。面對鑽法律漏洞質疑，他反駁表示身為律師，有社會義務讓民眾對這個議題了解。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://screenshots.firefoxusercontent.com/images/91b6d100-b3d1-4106-b79d-1bd37c430a2a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscreenshots.firefoxusercontent.com%2Fimages%2F91b6d100-b3d1-4106-b79d-1bd37c430a2a.png&h=e67d0bac&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n劉龍珠律師表示，當年聯邦政府大力掃蕩月子中心，令到外界有不少誤解，覺得有必要作出澄清；另外他也是月子中心掃蕩案中，部份孕婦的代理律師，親身經歷了整個審訊過程，有了第一手的資料，所以覺得自己最具發言權，要將這個「歷史真相」講出來。「現在已經有部份人意識到來美產子並不違法，可是對大部份民眾都是不了解，我寫這本書最本質不是一個選擇，而是一個法律的責任，一個社會責任和義務。」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://screenshots.firefoxusercontent.com/images/29d7669b-7e0f-42fe-a5ae-6740242b4316.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscreenshots.firefoxusercontent.com%2Fimages%2F29d7669b-7e0f-42fe-a5ae-6740242b4316.png&h=c9a8c6ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20171019/20187963\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20171019%2F20187963&d=QyXU194jRvXZQ7BW7U48Z9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=e2c8d1eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20171019%2F20187963&h=5f9ee9d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20171019/20187963</a></div>"},{"pid":"8b367ec5ec0778bd80a139349a11f7a5e22a6894","tid":444134,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T08:52:46.000Z","msg":"他希望藉着這本書告訴大家，來美產子並不違法，月子中心並不違法，在完全不違法的情況下，「你可以來美國大搖大擺的生，然後大搖大擺的走」，本身並沒有法律問題。他說，「來美生子應該是一個值得喜慶的大好事，並不應該作做小偷一樣，鬼鬼祟祟的不讓人看到。」<br />\n<br />\n不少人認為，赴美產子及月子中心只是存在法律灰色地帶，劉律師強調，「你要不（跟海關說）自己懷孕（合法），要不沒有懷孕（非法），沒有灰色地帶。」面對質疑，他表示不認為自己出書是鑽法律漏洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，反指法律上赴美產子是可行的，所以沒有洞可以鑽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"062c53d6b6ead56f9df7388c32a4938aba20a360","tid":444134,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T08:59:26.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://screenshots.firefoxusercontent.com/images/fc5190e6-1524-4e2c-b29e-d00891b352f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscreenshots.firefoxusercontent.com%2Fimages%2Ffc5190e6-1524-4e2c-b29e-d00891b352f2.png&h=90fa6bb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/10/19/3465362/20171018_ADUS_05AD_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F10%2F19%2F3465362%2F20171018_ADUS_05AD_w.mp4&d=QyXU194jRvXZQ7BW7U48Z9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=5646ff63\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/10/19/3465362/20171018_ADUS_05AD_w.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n</div><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/22/165751_81a70e0123f2bb3dc798ebebf24b1d96.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F22%2F165751_81a70e0123f2bb3dc798ebebf24b1d96.gif&h=9bad3a8d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/22/165752_f99467bfec193e1133916a68c68c1360.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F22%2F165752_f99467bfec193e1133916a68c68c1360.gif&h=61f11d76&s={SIZE}